value.title: StarCraft 2: ULTRALISKS VERSUS PROTOSS? (soO vs Zest)
value.excerpt: Ultralisks are uncommon in StarCraft 2 currently. In this professional match between Zest and soO, soO gets a solid advantage by focusing on Swarm Hosts
